name: Spearfish Canyon (Black Hills)
description:
Spearfish Canyon holds the majority of the substantial waterfalls in the Black Hills, however none of these form multi-drop canyons. The Devil's Bathtub hike contains some cool narrows with a pothole and the waterfalls are worthwhile to visit if looking for hikes. Spearfish Canyon is a unique place in the surrounding plains landscape.
